data.description: Welcome to this Beautiful Home located in excellent community with NO CDD!  Open concept home build in 2021, with 3 bedrooms, 2 baths, living room and dinning room combo. You will be impressed with the spacious kitchen with 42" gabinet, quartz countertops, pantry with all stailess steel appliances.  The comfortable master bedroom is located in the back of the home with amazing view of patio from the double windows. This suite has walk-in closet and bathroom with two sink, shower, separate toilet.  The huge fenced patio will give you the opportunity to enjoy with your family the excellent weather of Florida. The property include debt free solar panels.  Great Opportunity to join this exquisite area located minutes away from US-27 for easy and quick access to I-4 highway, restaurants, hospital, medical offices, supermarkets and mall. Call to see the property today!
